&amp;#125;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is really convenient, because now we have easy access to our data model documentation within our IDE as well as within any database explorer. And, liquibase &amp;amp; jOOQ ensure that they never go out of sync.&lt;/p&gt;
